File: A general view of the MTN 8 trophy. JOHANNESBURG - Orlando Pirates took a giant step towards reaching the MTN8 final after brushing bitter rivals Kaizer Chiefs aside in the semi-final first leg. Pirates beat Chiefs 3-0. Zakhele Lepasa got a rare start after an injury to Gabadinho Mhango and took it with both hands, scoring the first goal. Vincent Pule and man of the match Thembinkosi Lorch put the result beyond doubt.